title: Abigail Ratchford Goes Topless In Jaw-Dropping Photo
text:
Abigail Ratchford (Credit: Getty Images/Jonathan Leibson) 5423665 
Instagram superstar Abigail Ratchford shocked her millions of fans Sunday afternoon with a crazy topless photo. 
She captioned the black and white topless photo, “Things are not quite so simple always as black and white ; ).” (SLIDESHOW: 42 Times Arianny Celeste Went Topless O A photo posted by A b i g a i l (@abigailratchford) on Jan 15, 2017 at 12:13pm PST 
Ratchford is one of the most famous models in the world when it comes to social media, and she has garnered more than six million followers. Her Instagram is absolutely out of control. Click an image below for larger version.
